a2","tid":2004824,"uid":199502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T16:40:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">關於港字組</span></span><br />\n<br />\n奶間墮便ni！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1) <strong>（自以為）萬眾期待嘅GOOGLE SITE面世啦</strong>，個site大致上係一個目錄嚟，集合晒以前港字bbs譯過嘅正劇/trailers/ost歌詞/cover/花絮同spoilers片，大家唔想自己慢慢search就可以上去㩒，會直接link返入條片度嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/lihkg-2gethertheseries/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fview%2Flihkg-2gethertheseries%2F&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=15a0fdd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/view/lihkg-2gethertheseries/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2）<strong>我地嘅2gether fanart platform終於（唔太）隆重地開幕喇！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/2gethertheseries-fanarthk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fview%2F2gethertheseries-fanarthk&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=ed43e297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/view/2gethertheseries-fanarthk</a><br />\n<br />\n暫時我地開咗fan made video同埋fan fiction嘅corner，大家可以盡情享用各大巴絲、fans嘅創作！歡迎留低你對創作嘅comment，一齊交流吓！<br />\n<br />\n如果大家有更多2gether / BrightWin及其他演員嘅創作（包括但不限於sticker、插畫）想同大家分享，可以email入嚟同我地討論！<br />\n<br />\n以下係各款創作嘅處理：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>A) Fan Fiction ／插畫</strong></span><br />\n大家可以搵一個平台發表，將條<ins>可以觀看嘅 link send畀我地</ins>，或者<ins>直接原稿畀我地</ins>，我地會開subpage存放你嘅稿。<span style=\"color: orange;\">如果內容含攝伯b成人情節，請用其他平台發表</span>，然後send條link畀我地。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>B) Fan made video</strong></span><br />\n我地建議你<ins>upload去YouTube，然後send條link畀我地</ins>。如果你唔想擺上YouTube亦可以用<ins>google drive / email send條片畀我地</ins>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>C) Sticker</strong></span><br />\n我地建議你提供一張<ins>preview圖</ins>同埋<ins>可以download sticker嘅link</ins>畀我地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你想作者名一欄link去你個人facebook page / instagram亦可以同我地討論吓！<br />\n<br />\n3) <strong>由於港字人材輩出（無錯，我地賣花要讚下花香），<span style=\"color: orange;\">港字絲打</span>見大家寫得咁開心，執筆寫咗篇<span style=\"color: orange;\">Sarawat同Tine畢業後嘅fan fiction</span>，角度新鮮有趣，貼近時事，建議大家馬上入去website觀看！</strong><br />\n<br />\n4)  <strong>多謝大家支持，我地YouTube channel有破百訂閱喇！</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地channel會放港字組嘅創作同埋2gether 劇集playlist，未subscribe嘅快啲入嚟啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCviRRZkJqcBPR4So1Z_gL4Q?view_as=subscriber\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCviRRZkJqcBPR4So1Z_gL4Q%3Fview_as%3Dsubscriber&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=2fed4a9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCviRRZkJqcBPR4So1Z_gL4Q?view_as=subscriber</a><br />\n<br />\n我地暫時嘅創作有下面三條片，但創作係陸續有嚟的，敬請期待！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>泰國幪面超人</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9kTWW4ShqOg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9kTWW4ShqOg&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=e167c0d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9kTWW4ShqOg</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>勞斯萊斯</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/93E_ChrOhX0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F93E_ChrOhX0&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=35fe4d16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/93E_ChrOhX0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>強劍(泰文版)</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OEMpoiyofdw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOEMpoiyofdw&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=69fb26e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OEMpoiyofdw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港字組 上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nlihkg.kongjisubtitles@gmail.com"},{"pid":"8917bb0c90e2c31a69623d8b4b420548444ea04c","tid":2004824,"uid":199502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T16:40:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">泰文入門</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>感謝泰文巴打 @罩杯裏的豐波 嘅分享</strong><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>我其實斷斷續續叫學咗一年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都係靠自學，香港出面啲泰文班好似唔係幾掂<br />\n通常學泰文啲人都會話學咗點講先<br />\n字母遲啲再決定學唔學都得<br />\n但係我本人就比較痴線啲<br />\n一開波就學埋泰文字母聽字母歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DSIKJTW01NI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDSIKJTW01NI&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=168e9fa0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DSIKJTW01NI</a><br />\n留意返所謂泰文字母其實都係輔音嚟<br />\n通常泰國人串字母嗰陣都會幫佢哋加返個「o」音加個字母嘅例字<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.omniglot.com/images/writing/thai_cons.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.omniglot.com%2Fimages%2Fwriting%2Fthai_cons.gif&h=599be473&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係個字母歌我純粹當背歌仔冇認真記晒<br />\n一嚟有啲字(好似 ฐ ฏ)極少用<br />\n二嚟有啲字母例字香港人極少知係咩，對記字母冇幫助<br />\ne.g. ย個例字ยักษ์ =夜叉，屌你我十世都唔會用得著啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，咁就當背歌仔yo yak （ย  ยักษ์)就算<br />\n<br />\nYouTube 超強系列有個泰文字母介紹，想真係學認字母睇佢嗰幾條片都幾好<br />\n<br />\n書嘅話有本叫「泰文字母 聽&middot;說&middot;寫」都唔錯<br />\n但係我當佢係參考書咁睇<br />\n本嘢我認真用就淨係用咗頭幾個Chapter<br />\n知道大概個書寫系統點運作 (輔音字母+vowels+音調符號）<br />\n我就冇點再用本嘢  係間唔時有需要先再睇<br />\n<br />\n之後我就好似之前學其他language 咁<br />\n學咗啲成日用嘅basic verb，vocab同基本連接詞先<br />\n加埋啲現實例子睇人點用<br />\n然後迫自己用泰文寫佢出嚟，順便寫埋個羅馬拼音，有時就連埋個廣東話音<br />\n好似 「係」嘅泰文 ใช่，我就寫個羅馬音Ch&igrave; 同埋廣東話個音 「猜」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過廣東話個音都係輔助記，搵唔到唔洗夾硬搵<br />\n<br />\nYouTube我就睇超強系列（按：超強Scroll落去會有），佢啲example都幾生活化幾好笑<br />\n但係佢啲發音未必係最標準<br />\n如果識寫泰文字母就可以係Google Translate用佢個泰文手寫板寫返佢啲例子出嚟聽返個發音同搵返個羅馬拼音，再自己mark返低<br />\n<br />\nThaiPod101 我就當參考書咁用，有需要或者有邊個topic嘅泰文想學先睇，同埋聽佢啲Listening Comprehension <br />\n（按：ThaiPod101 Scroll落去會有）<br />\n<br />\n另外YouTube 我仲有睇嘅仲有哲哲 เจ๋อเจ๋อ<br />\n佢啲vlog 有埋泰文字幕用嚟抄vocab都唔錯<br />\n<br />\n其他就係睇劇同聽歌<br />\n再嘗試捉啲字出嚟<br />\n依排就係瘋狂睇2gether+聽Scrubb啲歌<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Qduuanuy704\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQduuanuy704&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=23e239f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Qduuanuy704</a><br />\n依個channel有scrubb嘅歌加埋唔完全標準嘅羅馬拼音，可以跟住唱<br />\n同埋可以將佢啲羅馬拼音對返泰文歌詞，就知點拆返開啲泰文句子出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學泰文都係同學其他一樣language一樣<br />\n聽完人哋講個音一次，個腦run一次個音，然後自己口講repeat多一次 （回音法）<br />\n<br />\n2gether個泰文名เพราะเราคู่กัน已經有兩個常用字學<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時我學嘅方法就係拆返開 เพราะ  เรา  คู่กัน<br />\nเพราะ - 因為 （常用基本字）<br />\nเรา - 我哋 （常用基本字）<br />\nคู่กัน- 好match嘅一對 （少用，google translate 個音思都唔太準）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後回音法repeat啲音，之後你睇劇聽歌或者其他泰文嘢就會慢慢catch到啲字<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰文Grammar超簡單，係發音同個書寫系統煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />發音個音調錯咗會好似廣東話咁意思會錯晒<br />\n<br />\n好似我哋個「喺」字咁<br />\n個音調掌握唔到發高咗會發咗做個「閪」字咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我哋有粵語底，掌握泰文音調會比其他國家嘅learner 有著數唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>感謝 P'@美人魚我合唱  提供</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">ThaiPod101</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pXV-MzO4Acs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpXV-MzO4Acs&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=3a7d3c3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pXV-MzO4Acs</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">超強系列</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GF5L4BanCXs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGF5L4BanCXs&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=38ec6e0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GF5L4BanCXs</a>"},{"pid":"aeb4eca35331d3afd9b1cf807fb68ad82afddef5","tid":2004824,"uid":199502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T16:41:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">巴絲自家製作品</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">連登港字組號外</span></strong><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n[號外] 港字組除咗更新字幕外，仲準備咗個彩蛋比大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不經不覺，連登港字組已經同大家一齊追劇追咗第十個星期！為咗令大家重溫返跳入泰劇大坑嘅感動，並且積極推廣泰國文化，港字組誠意邀請咗當紅嘅Sarawat同Tine友情出演 - 泰文版幪面超人主題曲！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事不宜遲，去片！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9kTWW4ShqOg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9kTWW4ShqOg&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=e167c0d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9kTWW4ShqOg</a><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Sarawatlism:</span></strong><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n今朝見到啲人話bright被啲終國人整到喊，真係好嬲，即刻整咗條片支持佢，有ac就得閒入嚟幫手retweet推吓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ying_yatsum/status/1249512051006779393?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"ht